channel.title: How many players?
channel.description:
I'm about to buy an VPS from VPSland.com that one that costs 24$ every month. What does it mean by "Price for 3 mth pre-payment: $23" Is it 23$ for 3 months 24/7 hosting or am I wrong? By the way, another question the one im about to buy has a RAM of 1040MB, Diskspace 10GB, Bandwidth 300GB how many players can it host withot lagging & disconnecting?
Best/Regards, Your Master
